    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hexo博客搭建"><a href="#Hexo博客搭建" class="headerlink" title="Hexo博客搭建"></a>Hexo博客搭建</h1><h3 id="1-安装nodejs"><a href="#1-安装nodejs" class="headerlink" title="1 安装nodejs"></a>1 安装nodejs</h3><p>去<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/" target="_blank" rel="external">nodejs官网</a>下载对应系统的安装包，按提示安装</p>
<p>检视安装成功</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">node -v</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="2-利用Hexo搭建博客"><a href="#2-利用Hexo搭建博客" class="headerlink" title="2 利用Hexo搭建博客"></a>2 利用Hexo搭建博客</h3><h4 id="2-1-创建博客目录"><a href="#2-1-创建博客目录" class="headerlink" title="2.1 创建博客目录"></a>2.1 创建博客目录</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo init dannyzhaoo.github.io</div><div class="line">cd dannyzhaoo.github.io</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="2-2-生成静态界面"><a href="#2-2-生成静态界面" class="headerlink" title="2.2 生成静态界面"></a>2.2 生成静态界面</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo clean  //如果是这个网页上有内容的最好就不要这步了</div><div class="line">hexo g</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>|g 即generate</p>
<h4 id="2-3-运行"><a href="#2-3-运行" class="headerlink" title="2.3 运行"></a>2.3 运行</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo s</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="3-配置文件"><a href="#3-配置文件" class="headerlink" title="3 配置文件"></a>3 配置文件</h3><p>这部分主要是指的是站点配置文件</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">title: 流光</div><div class="line">subtitle: 细数似水年华的美好</div><div class="line">description:</div><div class="line">author: DannyZhao</div><div class="line">language: zh-Hans   //如果没有设置，文章所有的字都不是简体中文</div><div class="line">timezone:</div><div class="line">url: http:/dannyzhaoo.github.io</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="4-更换一个好看的主题"><a href="#4-更换一个好看的主题" class="headerlink" title="4 更换一个好看的主题"></a>4 更换一个好看的主题</h3><h4 id="4-1-下载一个主题"><a href="#4-1-下载一个主题" class="headerlink" title="4.1 下载一个主题"></a>4.1 下载一个主题</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">git clone https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="4-2-网站的站点文件里设置"><a href="#4-2-网站的站点文件里设置" class="headerlink" title="4.2 网站的站点文件里设置"></a>4.2 网站的站点文件里设置</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">theme: next   //更换主题</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="5-部署到GitHub上"><a href="#5-部署到GitHub上" class="headerlink" title="5 部署到GitHub上"></a>5 部署到GitHub上</h3><h4 id="5-1-安装hexo-deployer-git"><a href="#5-1-安装hexo-deployer-git" class="headerlink" title="5.1 安装hexo-deployer-git"></a>5.1 安装<a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-deployer-git" target="_blank" rel="external">hexo-deployer-git</a></h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="5-2-网站配置文件"><a href="#5-2-网站配置文件" class="headerlink" title="5.2 网站配置文件"></a>5.2 网站配置文件</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">deploy:</div><div class="line">  type: git</div><div class="line">  repo: https://github.com/DannyZhaoo/DannyZhaoo.github.io</div><div class="line">  branch: master</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="5-3-部署"><a href="#5-3-部署" class="headerlink" title="5.3 部署"></a>5.3 部署</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo d</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="6-添加标签，分类"><a href="#6-添加标签，分类" class="headerlink" title="6 添加标签，分类"></a>6 添加标签，分类</h3><h4 id="6-1-网站的配置文件"><a href="#6-1-网站的配置文件" class="headerlink" title="6.1 网站的配置文件"></a>6.1 网站的配置文件</h4><p>一般下载下来就不用改了，都包含着</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">tag_dir: tags</div><div class="line">archive_dir: archives</div><div class="line">category_dir: categories</div><div class="line">code_dir: downloads/code</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="6-2-主题的配置文件"><a href="#6-2-主题的配置文件" class="headerlink" title="6.2 主题的配置文件"></a>6.2 主题的配置文件</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">menu:</div><div class="line">  home: /</div><div class="line">  categories: /categories</div><div class="line">  archives: /archives</div><div class="line">  tags: /tags</div><div class="line">  about: /about</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="6-3-新建tags和categories页面"><a href="#6-3-新建tags和categories页面" class="headerlink" title="6.3 新建tags和categories页面"></a>6.3 新建tags和categories页面</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo new page tags</div><div class="line">hexo new page categories</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="6-4-修改source下的tags-index-md和categories-index-md"><a href="#6-4-修改source下的tags-index-md和categories-index-md" class="headerlink" title="6.4 修改source下的tags/index.md和categories/index.md"></a>6.4 修改source下的tags/index.md和categories/index.md</h4><p>注意冒号是<strong>英文</strong>的。</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">title: tags</div><div class="line">date: 2017-06-02 16:48:54</div><div class="line">type: "tags"</div><div class="line">comments: false</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">title: categories</div><div class="line">date: 2017-06-02 16:48:48</div><div class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</div><div class="line">comments: false</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="7-主题配置"><a href="#7-主题配置" class="headerlink" title="7 主题配置"></a>7 主题配置</h4><h4 id="7-1-设置RSS"><a href="#7-1-设置RSS" class="headerlink" title="7.1 设置RSS"></a>7.1 设置RSS</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="7-2-设置代码高亮"><a href="#7-2-设置代码高亮" class="headerlink" title="7.2 设置代码高亮"></a>7.2 设置代码高亮</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"># Code Highlight theme</div><div class="line"># Available value: normal | night | night eighties | night blue | night bright   可以从这几种中进行选择</div><div class="line"># https://github.com/chriskempson/tomorrow-theme</div><div class="line">highlight_theme: normal</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="7-3-设置样式"><a href="#7-3-设置样式" class="headerlink" title="7.3 设置样式"></a>7.3 设置样式</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"># Schemes</div><div class="line">#scheme: Muse</div><div class="line">scheme: Mist</div><div class="line">#scheme: Pisces</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="7-4-建立站点时间"><a href="#7-4-建立站点时间" class="headerlink" title="7.4 建立站点时间"></a>7.4 建立站点时间</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">since: 2017</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="7-5-设置动画效果"><a href="#7-5-设置动画效果" class="headerlink" title="7.5 设置动画效果"></a>7.5 设置动画效果</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">use_motion: true  # 开启动画效果</div><div class="line">use_motion: false # 关闭动画效果</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="7-6-设置背景动画"><a href="#7-6-设置背景动画" class="headerlink" title="7.6 设置背景动画"></a>7.6 设置背景动画</h4><p>有<code>canvas_nest</code>或<code>three_waves</code>只能同时开启一种背景动画效果。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"># canvas_nest</div><div class="line">canvas_nest: true //开启动画</div><div class="line">canvas_nest: false //关闭动画</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"># three_waves</div><div class="line">three_waves: true //开启动画</div><div class="line">three_waves: false //关闭动画</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="7-7-修改个人介绍部分的图片"><a href="#7-7-修改个人介绍部分的图片" class="headerlink" title="7.7 修改个人介绍部分的图片"></a>7.7 修改个人介绍部分的图片</h4><p>要在next的source中images里添加一个图片</p>
