<h4 id="7-8-设置阅读全文"><a href="#7-8-设置阅读全文" class="headerlink" title="7.8 设置阅读全文"></a>7.8 设置阅读全文</h4><p>在主题配置文件中添加</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">auto_excerpt:</div><div class="line">  enable: true</div><div class="line">  length: 220</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="7-9-设置Favicon"><a href="#7-9-设置Favicon" class="headerlink" title="7.9 设置Favicon"></a>7.9 设置Favicon</h4><p>将图片放在站点的<code>source</code>下</p>
